        privacySection4InfoText: "Within the framework of the applicable legal provisions, you have the right to free information about your stored personal data, its origin and recipient and the purpose of data processing at any time, as well as a right to correction or deletion of this data. You can contact us at any time with regard to this and other questions on the subject of personal data.",
